                        </choice> 60</bibl>, stimulant <lb/>alcalia fibram <hi rendition="#u">contractilem</hi> et nerveam <lb/>falsch! <lb/>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>u</abbr>
                        <expan>und</expan>
                    </choice> die<bibl corresp="https://edition-humboldt.de/34M3MMHW"><persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0013266 http://d-nb.info/gnd/119187396"> Cullen</persName>’s
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>Lect.</abbr>
                            <expan>Lectures</expan>
                        </choice> on the <choice>
                            <abbr>Mater.</abbr>
